        "content": [
          {
            "kind": "Markdown",
            "markdown": "Sidebar failure reproduced with three concurrent compact reads: 2 success, 1 E2D-CLI-0002; single read stable at 882070 characters. Root cause: each TaskBoardDiskStore constructor takes exclusive .taskboard/.lock for recovery. Added InFlightRequestBroker keyed by workspace/executable, exact compact-read detection, settled release, and limited retry only for Taskboard is locked diagnostic. tasks get/mutations remain separate. Manifest container renamed Task Board, view Tasks. RED 24/26 → GREEN 26/26; typecheck GREEN; Extension Host exit 0. VSIX 9 files/17.93 KB installed stable 0.1.0. Docs/licenses GREEN. Visual control unavailable os error 3."
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
